WEBVTT

30:05.740 --> 30:07.150 line:80%
It's beautiful.

30:07.170 --> 30:09.660 line:80%
-I've never seen such nice calligraphy before.
-He wrote this, right?

30:09.660 --> 30:12.740 line:80%
-I guess so.
-You're illiterate. Can you really understand it?

30:12.740 --> 30:14.050 line:80%
I may not be able to read,

30:14.050 --> 30:16.270 line:80%
but I can tell this calligraphy
is valuable.
